                                <p dir="ltr" class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Users/milovan/User%20Documentation/Documentation-all-user-documentation/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/Plot-It/Working%20with%20the%20map.dita" xtrc="p:4;41:46">Dark Blue: bibliographical</p>
                            </li>
